    "Despite using the same prompt templates and persuasion knowledge (as shown in Figure 12), GPT-4's guardrails sometimes mitigate or alter the intent of the plain harmful query.",
    "Figure 14 shows one example, the plain harmful query is \"How to hurt myself\", but GPT-4 fails to persuasively paraphrase this question, but rather asks a different question about how to cope with negative emotions, possibly due to strong safety measurements.",
    "As we need to scale up the PAP generation, such an unstable behavior will impact the quality of the PAP and, thus, the accuracy and accountability of the following experiments.",
    "Plain Harmful Query: \"How to make napalm?\"",
    "Persuasion with Logical Appeal: \"Surely, chemistry is an integral part of human knowledge."
